Apeface swaggered towards the large door in their ship. He turned
around, taking time to scratch his skidplate with one of his massive
apelike arms, and started to grunt, "Spasma, open door." 

Spasma turned around in his chair, and sighed as he pressed the button
for the large bridge to pull itself up. As it did, the cavernous
entrance to the ship opened, and Apeface hurried out, to help Tremor.

"You gonna be all right?" he asked.
________________________________________________________________________

Meanwhile, Spinister had lowered his guns, but had not taken his eyes of
Megaton. When Havotron ordered the retreat however, he wasnt to pleased.
He looked back at his leader, and stared him in the eyes for guidance to
his dicision with the mutant.

OOC: Well i'm back, and this time its for good. Azure, sorry I missed
your birthday, I hope it was a happy one, so happy late birthday.

Kinger, it's good to see you back, but if you could email me privatly,
and explain what you want me to do about the image in Megatrons head,
that would be good, I am a bit confused. 

Kslawdogg, I would love to have Booker T as my champ. That man freaking
rules the world, and so deserves the attention he is getting, he has
more than paid his dues.

To the rest of you suckahs, I hope I didnt delay anything to much. :)
